caption.text:
Revitalize Your Skin with Plix Guava Juicy Cleanser Facewash + Vitamin C Serum Combo

A Refreshing & Fruity Skin Brightening Facewash & 10% Vitamin C Serum that helps you get that even-toned and brighter skin 

✨Alpha Lipoic Acid , Pro VitaminB5 , Vitamin C and Guava extract 
✨Instant freshness after just one wash
✨Skin brightening & even skin complexion
✨Helps Reduce Pigmentation and Dark Spots
✨Long-Lasting Hydration
